title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on All FIB Files Finales
content:
Once you move into the Darnell Bros Garment Factory, get acquainted with Jodi Marshall and you can embark on the clandestine operations of The FIB Files.

All FIB Files Finales — The Brute Force File, The Black Box File, The Fine Art File, and The Project Breakaway File — are paying out 2X GTA$ and RP this week. This boost also applies to this week’s Priority File (The Fine Art File).

Complete any three FIB Files Finales to fulfill the latest Weekly Challenge, and get a GTA$100,000 bonus.
